Url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/My-Kids-Lick-The-Bowl-Website-Header.jpg","width":640,"height":300,"caption":"My Kids Lick The Bowl"},"image":{"@id":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/#\/schema\/logo\/image\/"},"sameAs":["http:\/\/www.facebook.com\/mykidslickthebowl","https:\/\/x.com\/staceymklb","http:\/\/www.instagram.com\/my_kids_lick_the_bowl","http:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/stacey-kemeys","https:\/\/nz.pinterest.com\/KidFoodExpert\/"]},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/#\/schema\/person\/811751076c89b7aa27269ee6bdc8c237","name":"Stacey","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c8842d5a0b48c0f2b56f048b9ab1301d8288b7254746a260921919071d3f3b8d?s=96&d=mm&r=g","url":"https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c8842d5a0b48c0f2b56f048b9ab1301d8288b7254746a260921919071d3f3b8d?s=96&d=mm&r=g","contentUrl":"https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c8842d5a0b48c0f2b56f048b9ab1301d8288b7254746a260921919071d3f3b8d?s=96&d=mm&r=g","caption":"Stacey"},"sameAs":["https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/start-here\/","https:\/\/facebook.com\/mykidslickthebowl"],"url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/author\/stacey\/"},{"@type":"Recipe","name":"One Pan Pasta - Sausage Tomato & Lentils","author":{"@id":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/#\/schema\/person\/811751076c89b7aa27269ee6bdc8c237"},"description":"An easy one pan pasta recipe flavoured with sausage tomato and lentils a quick no fuss family dinner","datePublished":"2024-10-11T03:02:08+00:00","image":["https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/sausage-pasta-3.jpg","https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/sausage-pasta-3-500x500.jpg","https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/sausage-pasta-3-500x375.jpg","https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/sausage-pasta-3-480x270.jpg"],"video":{"name":"Sausage Pasta 1080 LS.mov","description":"This sausage pasta is an easy one pan recipe, The pasta literally cooks in the sauce which is made with sausages, tomatoes and lentils it is full of flavor and a great family meal.","thumbnailUrl":"https:\/\/content.jwplatform.com\/thumbs\/MuRG0xLi-720.jpg","contentUrl":"https:\/\/content.jwplatform.com\/videos\/MuRG0xLi.mp4","uploadDate":"2024-10-11T02:54:46+00:00","@type":"VideoObject"},"recipeYield":["6","6 serves"],"prepTime":"PT10M","cookTime":"PT35M","totalTime":"PT45M","recipeIngredient":["2 Tablespoons olive oil","1 large onion  (diced)","1 cup celery (diced)","1 cup carrots (diced)","3  sausages (225 grams)","3 cloves garlic (crushed)","1 Tablespoon thyme (dried)","400 grams crushed tomatoes (canned)","400 grams whole peeled tomatoes (canned)","400 grams lentils  (canned, 250 grams drained and rinsed.  )","2 cups stock (500 millilitres)","350 grams pasta (penne, 3 and a half cups)","3 handfuls baby spinach leaves (optional)"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Heat oil in the pan over a medium heat","name":"Heat oil in the pan over a medium heat","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the onion, celery, and carrot and sauté until beginning to soften (around 5 mins).","name":"Add the onion, celery, and carrot and sauté until beginning to soften (around 5 mins).","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Cut up the sausage meat into bite-sized pieces, add this to the pan and brown.","name":"Cut up the sausage meat into bite-sized pieces, add this to the pan and brown.","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the garlic cloves and thyme. Sauté everything for a further 1-2 minutes until you can smell the garlic.","name":"Add the garlic cloves and thyme. Sauté everything for a further 1-2 minutes until you can smell the garlic.","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add both tins of tomatoes, the lentils and the stock, give everything a good stir.","name":"Add both tins of tomatoes, the lentils and the stock, give everything a good stir.","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the dry pasta, stir, let the mix come to the boil, then cover with a lid and reduce the heat to low.  It should take around 25 mins for the pasta to become tender, but this will vary a little depending on the pasta shape you have chosen.","name":"Add the dry pasta, stir, let the mix come to the boil, then cover with a lid and reduce the heat to low.  It should take around 25 mins for the pasta to become tender, but this will vary a little depending on the pasta shape you have chosen.","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-5"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Optional: Add 2 to3  handfuls of baby spinach leaves to the pan, cover with the lid for 1-2 minutes until wilted, then stir through the pasta.","name":"Optional: Add 2 to3  handfuls of baby spinach leaves to the pan, cover with the lid for 1-2 minutes until wilted, then stir through the pasta.","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-6"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"If the pasta is not quite tender when you remove the lid, pop the lid back on and cook for a further couple of minutes. If the pasta sauce is thinner than you would prefer, cook the pasta for a few more minutes with the lid off so that extra moisture can escape.","name":"If the pasta is not quite tender when you remove the lid, pop the lid back on and cook for a further couple of minutes. If the pasta sauce is thinner than you would prefer, cook the pasta for a few more minutes with the lid off so that extra moisture can escape.","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-7"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Enjoy","name":"Enjoy","url":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#wprm-recipe-7141-step-0-8"}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"4.52","ratingCount":"39","reviewCount":"1"},"review":[{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"Loved this. I made it for my son in the UK with hidden veges. Can this be frozen, not that we had leftovers to freeze.  \r\nThanks.","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jan"},"datePublished":"2024-11-13"}],"recipeCategory":["Family Dinner Ideas"],"recipeCuisine":["Italian"],"keywords":"one pan pasta, pasta with lentils, sausage pasta, sausage pasta recipes, sausage tomato pasta","nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","servingSize":"1 g","calories":"687 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"98 g","proteinContent":"34 g","fatContent":"18 g","saturatedFatContent":"5 g","cholesterolContent":"31 mg","sodiumContent":"816 mg","fiberContent":"26 g","sugarContent":"10 g","transFatContent":"0.1 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"12 g"},"@id":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https:\/\/mykidslickthebowl.com\/one-pan-pasta-tomato-sausage-lentils\/"}]}</script>
