<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<p>This one pan <strong>Sausage Pasta</strong> with tomatoes and lentils is an easy and economical family dinner.</p>



<p>The humble sausage can make yummy family dinners, if you have more sausages in the fridge or freezer try my <a href="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/sausage-bake-one-tray/" data-wpel-link="internal">sausage bake</a> or <a href="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/fried-spaghetti/" data-wpel-link="internal">fried spaghetti</a>. </p>


<div class="wp-block-image aligncenter">
<figure class="size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3.jpg" alt="Sausage pasta in cast iron pan placed on benchtop, fresh spinach in a bowl and leaves scattered on the table." class="wp-image-25614" srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-3-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_84 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction">
