<div class="kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id6094_8210b4-71 alignnone ambassador-block-lt wp-block-kadence-rowlayout"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-mobile-layout-row kt-row-valign-top">

<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column6094_f71863-1b"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-how-to-make-this-recipe-suitable-for-baby-led-weaning"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="how_to_make_this_recipe_suitable_for_baby-led-weaning"></span>How To Make This Recipe Suitable For Baby-Led-Weaning<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>This recipe can be suitable for baby led weaning, choose a large pasta shape that is easy to grasp such as penne.</li>



<li>Ensure the pasta is cooked until soft.</li>



<li>Remove the skin from the sausages or slice them lengthways into quarters, as sausages and hotdogs are known chocking hazards when served in full rounds.  .</li>



<li>Choose a low salt stock.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

</div></div>


<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>


