0x480.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-8-360x240.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-8-180x120.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sausage-pasta-8-150x100.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
