 class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-unit" style="color: #323545">mg</span></span><span style="color: #323545"> | </span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-container wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-container-iron"><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-label  wprm-block-text-bold" style="color: #323545">Iron: </span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-value" style="color: #323545">9</span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-unit" style="color: #323545">mg</span></span></div></div>
