				<div class="comment-content">
					<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
Loved this. I made it for my son in the UK with hidden veges. Can this be frozen, not that we had leftovers to freeze.<br />
Thanks.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

