		<section id="block-7" class="widget widget_block"><style>.kb-image6dc8ca-d1 .kb-image-has-overlay:after{opacity:0.3;}</style>
<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image6dc8ca-d1 size-large"><img width="981" height="1024" decoding="async" src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/homepage-about-stacey-981x1024.jpg" alt="" class="kb-img wp-image-17399"/></figure>
</section><section id="block-8" class="widget widget_block"><style>.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading676d1d-01, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading676d1d-01[data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading676d1d-01"]{font-style:normal;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading676d1d-01 mark.kt-highlight, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading676d1d-01[data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading676d1d-01"] mark.kt-highlight{font-style:normal;color:#f76a0c;-webkit-box-decoration-break:clone;box-decoration-break:clone;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading676d1d-01 img.kb-inline-image, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading676d1d-01[data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading676d1d-01"] img.kb-inline-image{width:150px;vertical-align:baseline;}</style>
<h3 class="kt-adv-heading676d1d-01 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading676d1d-01">Hello, I’m Stacey!</h3>
</section><section id="block-9" class="widget widget_block widget_text">
<p>As a mum of four with a background in <strong>Human Nutrition and Dietetics</strong>, I know all to well that sometimes meal times can be stressful and that when it comes to their nutrition journey, not all kids are the same even when they grow up in the same family! I am here to support you with common sense <strong>evidence-based advice</strong> and <strong>fuss-free recipes.</strong></p>
</section><section id="block-10" class="widget widget_block"><link data-minify="1" rel='stylesheet' id='kadence-blocks-advancedbtn-css' href='https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/cache/min/1/wp-content/plugins/kadence-blocks/dist/style-blocks-advancedbtn.css?ver=1773428928' media='all' />
<style>.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kb-btns7c74d6-f3{padding-top:5px;gap:var(--global-kb-gap-xs, 0.5rem );justify-content:center;align-items:center;}.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-button{font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;}.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-right:5px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button{color:#555555;border-color:#555555;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{color:#ffffff;border-color:#444444;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button::before{display:none;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns7c74d6-f3 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{background:#444444;}</style>
<div class="wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn kb-buttons-wrap kb-btns7c74d6-f3"><style>ul.menu .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kb-btn035558-1f.kb-button{width:initial;}</style><a class="kb-button kt-button button kb-btn035558-1f kt-btn-size-standard kt-btn-width-type-auto kb-btn-global-inherit  kt-btn-has-text-true kt-btn-has-svg-false  wp-block-button__link wp-block-kadence-singlebtn" href="/start-here"><span class="kt-btn-inner-text">ABOUT</span></a></div>
</section><section id="block-11" class="widget widget_block">
